;;; A GME (General Monomial Expression has the form:
;;;      c1 c2 ... cr x1^n1 x2^n2 ... xm^nm
;;; where (free-of ci xj) holds and nj are non-negative integers.

;;; A GPE (General Polynomial Expressions) is either
